 and distinguishing real and fake\nvideos. Our extensive experiments on standard benchmarks demonstrate that Mover\nis highly effective.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 May 2023 07:30:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-11"}
