able although the thickness is taken in a\nlarger range with increasing intensity. This work predicts that near future RPA\nexperiments with 10-100 PW facilities will enter a new regime with the\nadjustable and large-range foil thickness for steady acceleration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 May 2023 10:28:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-11"}
