otpoint switching resulting from the reconnection\nallows the coronal dimming to intrude onto the boundary of the southern polar\ncoronal hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 May 2023 12:45:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-11"}
